### ===========================
### AUTH - Pruebas de endpoints
### ===========================
### Usar con REST Client (VS Code) o Thunder Client
### Reemplazar {{TOKEN}} con el token real del login/register

### 1. Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Obtener perfil (requiere token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 4. Actualizar perfil
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "username": "newusername"
}

### 5. Eliminar cuenta
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/auth/account
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
